<HEADLINE> Capitals Klee Signs Three-Year Deal  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- Ken Klee avoided arbitration Wednesday and
signed a three-year, $4.25 million contract with the Washington
Capitals.
</P>
<P>
   The 29-year-old defenseman has spent his entire career in the
Capitals organization. Last season, he had seven goals and 13
assists.
</P>
