<HEADLINE> Mary Lou Retton Has Third Child  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   HOUSTON (AP) -- Sixteen years after she won an Olympic gold
medal, Mary Lou Retton has no intention of slowing down.
</P>
<P>
   Retton, 32, gave birth to her third daughter, Skyla Brae Kelley,
on Aug. 9, and recently completed a promotional tour for her book,
