   Retton and her husband, Shannon Kelley, have two other
daughters, Shayla Rae, 5, and McKenna Lane, 3.
</P>
<P>
   Retton, a native of Fairmont, W.Va., won the women's all-around
gold medal in gymnastics at the 1984 Olympic Games in Los Angeles.
She now lives in Houston.
