anywhere.''
</P>
<P>
   Making the 20-acre Blue Rose Estate public would require a
zoning change.
</P>
<P>
   Neither Brooks nor his wife attended the meeting.
</P>
<P>
   Country music stars Conway Twitty, Loretta Lynn and Dolly Parton
already have created tourist attractions near their Tennessee
homes, and Elvis Presley's Graceland complex draws more than
600,000 visitors a year.
</P>
