<HEADLINE> By The Associated Press  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   Friday's forecast calls for clouds and showers
statewide with
high in the upper 60s. Rain is likely Friday night in the east
where the low will be in the upper 50s. The western part of the
state will see a few showers and a low from 50 to 55.
